## Do Not

- Do not install page builder plugins (Elementor, Divi, etc.)
- Do not use `update_option()` for per-user data — use user meta
- Do not hardcode URLs — always use `home_url()`, `get_template_directory_uri()`, etc.
- Do not commit `node_modules/` or `assets/dist/`
- Do not modify WordPress core files
- Do not use `extract()` in templates
- Do not store credit card or payment data locally
